Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,中_置顶,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,中_置顶,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.63,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.98,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:09.99,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:15.50,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you kill your friends, if you can fulfill your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.99,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you die for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.13,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:26.39,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Life is a game It's a survival That's right! How do you start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:31.89,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Time and Space It's a crossroad through a gate! Where do you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.42,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.58,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you need to live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:41.55,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.83,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.73,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:49.74,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:54.61,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.12,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:59.77,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.82,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.97,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:12.57,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.63,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,帶刺的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.98,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你的故事裡認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:09.99,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,恨之深皆因愛之切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:15.50,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你會為一己之利置朋友於死地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.99,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你會為了他人而犧牲自我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.13,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,它們又有何區別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:26.39,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！人生就是生存遊戲　你要如何開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:31.89,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,時間和空間是分岔路口　你要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.42,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,尋求永生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.58,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但生存的意義又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:41.55,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並不知道世界的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.83,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是時空的亂入者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.73,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,世界不會因你而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:49.74,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,規則才決定著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:54.61,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，我們憑著愛穿越古今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.12,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,爆發吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:59.77,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.82,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.97,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在奇蹟之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:12.57,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是終結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:42.89,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:47.93,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,高鳴る鼓動許される?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:59.23,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会いたくて涙 溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:04.83,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全ては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:12.45,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,崩れる身体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:24.86,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一度君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:42.89,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟還要失去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:47.93,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,這劇烈的心悸方能被寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:59.23,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,想要見到你 想到熱淚盈眶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:04.83,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是連接著未來的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:12.45,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,感到崩壞身體的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:24.86,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意 再一次守護你 許下誓言
